● Great question — let me clarify how these three relate:                                                                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
  The Three Layers                                                                                                                                                                                                     
   
  ┌──────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┐                                                              
  │      Entity      │                                             Purpose                                              │             Scope             │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────┤                                                              
  │ GodownStock      │ Master warehouse stock (running total)                                                           │ Always current, not per-shift │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────┤
  │ CashierStock     │ Counter display stock (running total)                                                            │ Always current, not per-shift │                                                              
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────┤                                                              
  │ ProductInventory │ Daily/shift-level tracking — openStock, incomeStock, totalStock, closeStock, sales, rate, amount │ Per shift                     │                                                              
  └──────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────┘                                                              
                  
  What goes in the Shift Closing Report?                                                                                                                                                                               
                  
  ProductInventory is the one that belongs in the shift report. It tracks:                                                                                                                                             
  - openStock — what you started the shift with
  - incomeStock — stock received during the shift (transfers from godown)                                                                                                                                              
  - totalStock — open + income                                           
  - closeStock — what's left at shift end                                                                                                                                                                              
  - sales — total - close (what was sold)
  - rate & amount — value of sales                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
  This mirrors exactly how TankInventory (dip readings) and NozzleInventory (meter readings) work for fuel — they're all per-shift snapshots.                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
  So the relationship is:                                                                                                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
  GodownStock      = warehouse master stock (like a bank account balance)                                                                                                                                              
  CashierStock     = counter master stock (like cash in register)                                                                                                                                                      
  ProductInventory = shift-level movement log (like a daily transaction statement)                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
  GodownStock/CashierStock are the current state. ProductInventory is the per-shift audit trail that feeds into the closing report.                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
